### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@salesApi = {{baseUrl}}/api/sales

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Get all orders (paginated)
GET {{salesApi}}/orders?Page=1&PageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all orders with filters
GET {{salesApi}}/orders?CustomerId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&Status=Pending&Page=1&PageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get order by ID
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
GET {{salesApi}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new order
POST {{salesApi}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "orderLines": [
    {
      "productId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
      "productName": "Sample Product",
      "unitPrice": 19.99,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa7",
      "productName": "Another Product",
      "unitPrice": 29.99,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Update order status
@orderIdToUpdate = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
PUT {{salesApi}}/orders/{{orderIdToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Processing"
}

### Update order status to Completed
PUT {{salesApi}}/orders/{{orderIdToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Completed"
}

### Update order status to Canceled
PUT {{salesApi}}/orders/{{orderIdToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Canceled"
}
